sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant R as Runtime
  participant CP as Control Plane
  participant RES as Resolver
  participant KA as Kernel Adapter
  participant EA as Execution Adapter
  participant L as Evidence Ledger

  U->>R: input
  R->>CP: RunRequest
  CP->>CP: context clear
  CP->>RES: resolve(policy, binding)
  RES-->>CP: effective config
  CP->>KA: rebuild working / query memory
  KA-->>CP: working candidates / citations
  CP->>CP: pre-check(policy, capability, working)
  CP->>EA: execute(No-LLM or approved adapter)
  EA-->>CP: result + citations
  CP->>CP: citation validate + fail-closed
  CP->>L: atomic commit
  L-->>CP: evidence_id
  CP->>CP: update working.json
  CP-->>R: RunAccepted or RunRejected
  R-->>U: output
